Phase 4: Quiz Engine and Weak Area Detection

- Quiz generation API (/api/quiz) with Ambiguity Training Mode for CISSP (scenario, best-answer, risk-prioritization, governance, management questions)
- Quiz submission/scoring API (/api/quiz/submit) with weak area identification
- Weak area analysis API (/api/analyze-weakness) aggregates quiz history into per-domain progress, computes streaks, identifies weak domains below 70%
- Quiz UI at /dashboard/quiz with setup (type, domain, count), question flow with per-question feedback (correct/incorrect highlighting, explanation, competing analysis), and results summary with score circle and weak area tags
- Quizzes dashboard card wired to /dashboard/quiz

